      <title>法国和意大利的通货膨胀使欧洲央行继续走低利率之路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/french-inflation-slows-to-lowest-level-since-august-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国通货膨胀率2.5年来首次降至3%以下，意大利公布的数据低于预期，证实了欧洲央行倾向于降息的趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-29/french-inflation-slows-to-lowest-level-since-august-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 07:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
